name: print + press, 06
description:
This is the sixth set in a year long monthly collaboration for print+press.
The first piece in the set is a 5"x7" screen print featuring an original design by Chelsea Parker Guidry. Each print is hand pressed and signed.
The second piece is a 5"x7" photography print on Fujicolor Crystal Archive Paper shot by Abby Powell Thompson.It has a matte finish, a small white border and is signed by the artist.
The pieces come packaged in a numbered vellum enclosure. Only twenty five of this month's were printed and only twenty are currently available.
